{
  "page": "Lord Swyft",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Swyft\" title=\"House Swyft\"><img alt=\"House Swyft.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/42/House_Swyft.svg/50px-House_Swyft.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/42/House_Swyft.svg/75px-House_Swyft.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/42/House_Swyft.svg/100px-House_Swyft.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Lord Swyft</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Swyft\" title=\"House Swyft\"><img alt=\"House Swyft.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/42/House_Swyft.svg/50px-House_Swyft.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/42/House_Swyft.svg/75px-House_Swyft.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/42/House_Swyft.svg/100px-House_Swyft.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nLord of <a href=\"/index.php/Cornfield\" title=\"Cornfield\">Cornfield</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Lord_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Lord-1\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Swyft\" title=\"House Swyft\">House Swyft</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">Greens</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Gods_Eye\" title=\"Gods Eye\">Gods Eye</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Princess_and_the_Queen\" title=\"The Princess and the Queen\">The Princess and the Queen</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lord Swyft</b> was the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Cornfield\" title=\"Cornfield\">Cornfield</a> and head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Swyft\" title=\"House Swyft\">House Swyft</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Swyft&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lord Swyft declared for the <a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">greens</a> during the Dance of the Dragons. He was part of the westermen host led by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Lannister\" title=\"Jason Lannister\">Jason Lannister</a> then by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Adrian_Tarbeck\" title=\"Adrian Tarbeck\">Adrian Tarbeck</a> and Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Lefford\" title=\"Humfrey Lefford\">Humfrey Lefford</a>. He was one of the two thousand men who died in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_by_the_Lakeshore\" title=\"Battle by the Lakeshore\">battle by the Lakeshore</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Swyft&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Lord-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Lord_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">At the start of the series, House Swyft is a knightly house holding the title of \"Knight of Cornfield\". As this character is described as a \"Lord\", it is possible the Swyfts were once a lordly house who held the title of \"Lord of Cornfield\".</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Swyft&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Triumphant.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Cornfield\" title=\"Cornfield\">Cornfield</a> </b><br />?–<a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Next known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Harys_Swyft\" title=\"Harys Swyft\">Harys Swyft</a> </b><br /><small><i><b>as <a href=\"/index.php/Knight_of_Cornfield\" title=\"Knight of Cornfield\">Knight of Cornfield</a> </b></i></small>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403194452\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.074 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.272 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 813/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12619/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7425/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1190/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1674/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.180/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.55 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  262.070      1 -total\n 92.44%  242.247      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 91.62%  240.119      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.36%   32.392     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.65%   